  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.poster.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.webm?t=1621176210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.mp4?t=1621176210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ANIME ARENA: INFINITE WAR</strong> is a unique action RPG game with survival elements. Zombies are everywhere and you are the only one who can defeat them! Take a cute anime girl under your control and fight against hordes of zombies. Earn money and gain experience to buy various upgrades and perks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/4dddda9d24b53ca6bc72e312c5d8c186.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>MIGHTY BOSSES</strong><br>Defeat all super bosses to complete your goal. And be sure it won't be easy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/7c57064569ca2586e17962de2c68cbdc.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>ZOMBIES ZOMBIES ZOMBIES</strong><br>Fight your way through the 50 unique zombie enemies. They could be funny and silly but still are very deadly!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/9bb615d1f1855dd9e62aa5be6ed0ba7b.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>CUSTOMIZATION AND EMOTES</strong><br>Dress up your girl as you like! Clothes, outfit, color and even bikini. Combinations are limitless! <br>Also defeat small bosses to unlock various emotes. Let your anime girl be truly alive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f408be8edb0d441297a8fdbc704e2f4a.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=172 /></span><br><strong>PERKS AND UPGRADES</strong><br>Your power is infinite. Buy upgrades with money or perks with level ups and become the most powerful anime girl!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/b1a9260f8e1454b2eaaee3cfd3f7e1d8.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=324 /></span><br><strong>ANIME STYLE</strong><br>Everybody loves cute anime girls! Take one under your control and let the others be your companions. <br><br><strong>INFINITE MODE</strong><br>Test your skills against an infinite waves of zombies in this special mode. How long could you survive?<br><br><strong>BLOODY ARENA</strong> <br>Kill dozens of zombies with a single sword hit. Make these ragdoll dummies fly off with fountains of blood!<br><br><strong>HARDCORE ARENA</strong><br>Your every movement and action matters when enemies outnumber you. This arena won't spare you!<br><br><strong>DOUBLE SOUNDTRACK</strong><br>Two soundtracks in a single game! What would you choose, hard rock rhythms or relaxing ambient music?<br><br><strong>500 LEVELS</strong><br>Survive on 500 levels and kill all super bosses to defeat this zombie threat once and for all!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.poster.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.webm?t=1621176210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f1fee1de578bddf93f7e1af35b0f7b0f.mp4?t=1621176210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ANIME ARENA: INFINITE WAR</strong> is a unique action RPG game with survival elements. Zombies are everywhere and you are the only one who can defeat them! Take a cute anime girl under your control and fight against hordes of zombies. Earn money and gain experience to buy various upgrades and perks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/4dddda9d24b53ca6bc72e312c5d8c186.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>MIGHTY BOSSES</strong><br>Defeat all super bosses to complete your goal. And be sure it won't be easy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/7c57064569ca2586e17962de2c68cbdc.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>ZOMBIES ZOMBIES ZOMBIES</strong><br>Fight your way through the 50 unique zombie enemies. They could be funny and silly but still are very deadly!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/9bb615d1f1855dd9e62aa5be6ed0ba7b.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=266 /></span><br><strong>CUSTOMIZATION AND EMOTES</strong><br>Dress up your girl as you like! Clothes, outfit, color and even bikini. Combinations are limitless! <br>Also defeat small bosses to unlock various emotes. Let your anime girl be truly alive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/f408be8edb0d441297a8fdbc704e2f4a.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=172 /></span><br><strong>PERKS AND UPGRADES</strong><br>Your power is infinite. Buy upgrades with money or perks with level ups and become the most powerful anime girl!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510600/extras/b1a9260f8e1454b2eaaee3cfd3f7e1d8.avif?t=1621176210\" width=600 height=324 /></span><br><strong>ANIME STYLE</strong><br>Everybody loves cute anime girls! Take one under your control and let the others be your companions. <br><br><strong>INFINITE MODE</strong><br>Test your skills against an infinite waves of zombies in this special mode. How long could you survive?<br><br><strong>BLOODY ARENA</strong> <br>Kill dozens of zombies with a single sword hit. Make these ragdoll dummies fly off with fountains of blood!<br><br><strong>HARDCORE ARENA</strong><br>Your every movement and action matters when enemies outnumber you. This arena won't spare you!<br><br><strong>DOUBLE SOUNDTRACK</strong><br>Two soundtracks in a single game! What would you choose, hard rock rhythms or relaxing ambient music?<br><br><strong>500 LEVELS</strong><br>Survive on 500 levels and kill all super bosses to defeat this zombie threat once and for all!",
